</disciplines><abstract>&lt;p&gt;The transition from being considered a “person with a disability” to a “retired individual” is becoming an increasingly important issue worth more study. This brief focuses on this pivotal transition in a person’s life and discusses issues for BPA&amp;O and PABSS practitioners.&lt;/p&gt;</abstract>
